  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Apps for Processing Financial Transactions</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio0f19c55368511d4be10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Apps for Processing Financial Transactions</h1><div class=\"body\">\n<p class=\"p\">Here you find the apps and functions available for the handling of the different kinds of financial transaction:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"loio0f19c55368511d4be10000000a174cb4__ul_dfp_tsx_r1b\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">The general functions <a class=\"xref\" href=\"97908c53cc93ed23e10000000a174cb4.html\">Create Financial Transaction</a> (app ID\n<span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">FTR_CREATE</span>), <a class=\"xref\" href=\"1519c55368511d4be10000000a174cb4.html\">Process Financial Transaction</a> (app ID\n<span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">FTR_EDIT</span>), <a class=\"xref\" href=\"82017a294df345b499524973276bdbe8.html\">Manage Financial Transactions</a> (app ID\n<span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">F6157</span>), and <a class=\"xref\" href=\"2419c55368511d4be10000000a174cb4.html\">Collective Processing: Transaction Management</a> (transaction <span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">FTR_00</span>) that can be used\nfor creating and editing every kind of financial transaction.</p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"7b9aecdd2bcf4c3f8f9be9db2cd1e197.html\">Change Counterparties for Financial Transactions</a></p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"fd862b6e3d1d4afdb6cf51bca7c0f95b.html\">Display Financial Transactions with Changed Counterparty</a></p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"3919c55368511d4be10000000a174cb4.html\">Reference</a></p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"3619c55368511d4be10000000a174cb4.html\">Netting</a></p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"511c5f22c3db2919e10000000a421bc1.html\">Adjust Variable Rates/Prices</a></p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p><a class=\"xref\" href=\"b515da531198434de10000000a174cb4.html\">Updating Planned Records</a></p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"ac14da531198434de10000000a174cb4.html\">Rate Fixing</a></p></li>\n</ul>\n</div><div class=\"related-links\"> </div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
